	dprr:hasNoteText "J. Suolahti suggests that his rank in the concilium of L. Cornelius Lentulus Crus, Cos. 49, in Asia that year as listed in Josephus (AJ 14.229, 238) was either quaestor or military tribune (Arctos 2, 1958, 152-163).\n" .
